<p>I also had similar issues, and the following seems to work:</p>

<p>This deletes the local branch:</p>

<pre><code>git branch -d the_local_branch
</code></pre>

<p>This removes the remote branch</p>

<pre><code>git push origin :the_remote_branch
</code></pre>

<p><a href="http://makandracards.com/makandra/621-git-delete-a-branch-local-or-remote" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Source: Makandra Cards</a></p>
